    Convert VSMdata object to data.frame()

    vsm.data.frame.Rd

    Convert VSMdata object to data.frame()

    vsm.data.frame(obj)

    Arguments

    obj

    VSMdata object

    Value

    data frame with VSM data

    Author

    Thomas Gredig

    Examples

    filename = vsm.getSampleFiles()[1]
d = vsm.import(filename)
#> 32
q = vsm.data.frame(d)
